<para id="para-00004">In addition to databases, registries are available to provide guidance and information. <term id="term-00006">Registries</term> are collections of information regarding people and typically outline a specific condition or diagnosis (National Institutes of Health [NIH], 2023). <link target-id="table-00002" document="m00156"/> provides examples of commonly used registries and resources for nurses.</para>
