<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left">Autoimmune Registry</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left">Provides a hub for statistics, research, and client data for all autoimmune diseases. The goal of this registry is to support research and reduce time of diagnosis for clients while establishing appropriate funding for autoimmune disease treatment.<newline/> 
